OL,6,FA man who killed his partner after
OL,7,Finflicting over 100 injuries on her
OL,8,Fhas been given a life sentence for
OL,9,Fmurder.
OL,11,FStephen Todd left "tiny" Melissa
OL,12,FEastick, who was frail and vulnerable,
OL,13,Fwith around 123 bruises, cuts,
OL,14,Ffractures and cigarette burns, which
OL,15,Fwere caused during repeated assaults
OL,16,Fat his home.
