OL,6,FNewcastle Crown Court heard 36-year-
OL,7,Fold Melissa had suffered a brain
OL,8,Finjury which would have left her
OL,9,Funconscious for "some days" before her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FHe finally called 999 at around 7am on
OL,13,FTuesday, October 17, 2023, claiming he
OL,14,Fhad found Melissa unresponsive inside
OL,15,Fhis address on Stockton Terrace in
OL,16,FGrangetown.
OL,18,FShe was pronounced dead at the scene.
