OL,6,FTodd was arrested and later charged
OL,7,Fwith murder which he initially denied.
OL,8,FHe went on trial at Newcastle Crown
OL,9,FCourt but pleaded guilty to murder on
OL,10,Fthe third day.
OL,12,FTodd, of Buttermere Street,
OL,13,FSunderland, appeared before the same
OL,14,Fcourt on Wednesday 6 November where he
OL,15,Fwas handed a life sentence, with a
OL,16,Fminimum term of 21 years and four
OL,17,Fmonths in prison.
