OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement from
OL,7,FMelissa's family, they spoke of their
OL,8,Fpain of losing "a sister, a mother, an
OL,9,Faunty and a much-loved member" of
OL,10,Ftheir family.
OL,12,FHer family said when Melissa started a
OL,13,Frelationship with Todd, they felt like
OL,14,Fthey "had lost her" and struggled to
OL,15,Fmake contact or know where she was.
