OL,6,FDespite this, Melissa had been spotted
OL,7,Fin July last year while Todd was in
OL,8,Fprison for assaulting her, with her
OL,9,Ffamily saying, "she seemed happy." A
OL,10,Ffew months later they were all left
OL,11,F"shocked and devastated" after finding
OL,12,Fout from police that Melissa had
OL,13,Flikely been murdered.
OL,15,FThey said: "We felt so sorry for her
OL,16,Fhaving a bad start to her life ` and
OL,17,Fthat it continued throughout her life.
