OL,6,F"As a family we have tried our best,
OL,7,Fto tell her we love her and try and
OL,8,Fget her back on track, but she'd
OL,9,Falways find her way back to Todd.
OL,11,F"We are now traumatised by this and
OL,12,Fwish we'd done more. Melissa was a
OL,13,Fmuch-loved member of the family who
OL,14,Fwas taken too soon."
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police have urged anyone
OL,17,Fin a similar position to Miss Eastick
OL,18,Fto come forward, vowing to put the
OL,19,Fperpetrators before the court.
