OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Louise Jenkins, of
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police, said: "Our
OL,9,Fthoughts remain with Melissa's loved
OL,10,Fones as they continue to come to terms
OL,11,Fwith their loss.
OL,13,F"While nothing can bring Melissa back,
OL,14,FI do hope the sentencing handed down
OL,15,Ftoday brings her family some sense of
OL,16,Fclosure knowing that Todd is behind
OL,17,Fbars for a significant period.
