OL,6,F"Domestic abuse, no matter the form it
OL,7,Ftakes, is completely unacceptable and
OL,8,Fwe are committed to putting
OL,9,Fperpetrators before the courts.
OL,11,F"If any part of this case sounds
OL,12,Ffamiliar, to you or someone you know,
OL,13,Fwe would urge you to seek support at
OL,14,Fthe earliest opportunity."
